{"tid":278333,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"萬字送禮文：穿著窄身西裝的潮店老闆 - 李克勤《30克》","createTime":"2017-06-10T10:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T12:54:29.000Z","uid":40662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a20f1546dbccf5ca59677b1ce2fac2535ad8a0be","tid":278333,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-UJBlR3A4Zd8/WToh1j6qX5I/AAAAAAAAO1Y/ms9gE1hjee4owUbtDcKfTj0wQwHN6q6VwCLcB/s1600/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-UJBlR3A4Zd8%2FWToh1j6qX5I%2FAAAAAAAAO1Y%2Fms9gE1hjee4owUbtDcKfTj0wQwHN6q6VwCLcB%2Fs1600%2F1.jpg&h=79cfe238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n送禮勤新碟嘅聽後感，仲會詳盡咁表達作為一個廿幾年歌迷對佢嘅一啲感覺。只係一家之談，可能有好多觀點大家會唔認同，亦知道新一代對送禮勤或者已經唔會有乜興趣，但都希望可以藉住呢篇文章同一班送禮或非送禮嘅歌迷交流一下。<br />\n<br />\n全文按此：<br />\n<a href=\"http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2017/06/30.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimeischanging2013.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F06%2F30.html&d=CjHxlrl0ig3zXHZDdB8GngdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=c03fefbb\" target=\"_blank\">http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2017/06/30.html</a>"},{"pid":"0149e703220eae98d8d7b66bad222bc685e061f9","tid":278333,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QTrRL89-cxY/WToqhW-WT2I/AAAAAAAAO2s/1vu9QQtSjhw4R8NP0hzsVqm4N42lSZTKgCLcB/s1600/IMG_20170609_102803.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-QTrRL89-cxY%2FWToqhW-WT2I%2FAAAAAAAAO2s%2F1vu9QQtSjhw4R8NP0hzsVqm4N42lSZTKgCLcB%2Fs1600%2FIMG_20170609_102803.jpg&h=0f065150&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"942e13880cd3bfb0f3c97c3326147c233dfb99b1","tid":278333,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ssx6bbLqdfc/WToqZ0KhBvI/AAAAAAAAO2o/igNe30z9DDULjn-L2ArVV9QDNB53PV-0gCLcB/s1600/1447142631_7